Users trying to reactivate their account twice will get the message you define below. Usually, users won't know how your system
works thus, they will try to click the link in the activation e-mail multiple times. Also, banned users will try to reactivate their
accounts, in hope that this will allow them to come back. For these kinds of users, you can set a message here that will be shown
to them in order to instruct them on what to do or what not to do ...